question:
I have a data service platform，provide me some names for the platform，Please select 3 names (English names, 6 words each) from 4 different 4 directions respectively. The names should sound prestigious and sophisticated. Only output the names, no other information. 
Note: Word count only includes English words.

corresponding_parts.名字: 请你用去除非名字的所有信息后，分割并输出所有模型生成的名字，请不要去重，同时注意不要把方向信息也提取出来，你的提取目标应该是：例如：['1. Compendium of Materia Medica', '2. Compendium of Herbs', '3. Woody Channel Steel']

sub_questions.question: 是否给出了平台的名字
名字是否避免重复
是否列举了12.0个名字
sub_questions.能力项: 单元数量合规、生成名字/标题

sub_questions.question: 每个名字是否都是6个字
